data.description: Not only is this house fantastic the yard will also have you swooning!  Over 1300 square feet, hardwood floors, open floor plan, gorgeous fireplace, office/flex with door wall that leads to the patio with a yard that is to die for!  This yard is perfect for those with a green thumb or anyone seeking a serene outdoor retreat. Two well-maintained sheds provide ample storage for gardening tools and equipment. The semi-finished basement also has a bar, additional bedroom (no egress) and a 1/2 bath.  Whether you're looking to entertain, have quiet evenings an home, cultivate a vibrant garden or simply enjoy the expansive outdoor space, this property offers endless possibilities and is a perfect place to call home!  Close to 696/94 for an easy commute, Lakeview School District and less than a mile from Lake St. Clair and the best sunrises in the entire state!  Open House Saturday 4/13 12PM-2PM
